*libcanberra-0.11-r5 (28 Mar 2009)

  28 Mar 2009; Ulrich Mueller <ulm@gentoo.org>
  +files/libcanberra-0.11-dont-crash-without-display.patch,
  -libcanberra-0.9.ebuild, -libcanberra-0.10.ebuild,
  +libcanberra-0.11-r5.ebuild:
